meaning_str.bing:
n. 存在；生活方式；实有
网络. 生存；存在性；实在

存在；生存；实在；生活方式；实体；现实；存在物；物质存在；个体存在；生命状态

1.en: Similarly, it shall apply, in the case of the accession of new countries, to patents in existence on either side at the time of accession.
1.cn: 在有新国家加入的情况下，本规定应同样适用于加入时各方面已经存在的专利。

2.en: He claimed to know of the existence of a mysterious country called Sugarcandy Mountain, to which all animals went when they died.
2.cn: 他声称存在一个神奇的国度叫做糖果山，所有的动物死后都会去那里。

3.en: While Intel did not dispute the existence of a discount program, it maintained that it was not illegal and did not distort competition.
3.cn: 虽然英特尔没有争端存在的折扣计划它认为这是不合法的，不扭曲市场竞争。

0.en: So what proof do we have of its existence?
0.cn: 我们该如何印证车子的存在？

1.en: I don't understand. Their existence is conditional?
1.cn: 我不明白，卧室的存在有条件的吗？

2.en: These Infinity Stones each control an essential aspect of existence.
2.cn: 这些无限宝石每一颗都控制一种存在的必要方面。

3.en: Do you think the animal is contemplating its own existence?
3.cn: 你认为她是在刷存在感吗？

4.en: I wasn't even aware of its existence until yesterday. I'm not talking about its existence. I'm talking about what it depicts.
4.cn: 到昨天为止我都不知道它的存在。我不是问录像的存在，我是问里面的内容。

5.en: Why hast thou forsaken me, O deity whose existence I doubt?
5.cn: 神啊，我一直怀疑你的存在，你为何抛弃我？

6.en: Making their master happy was the tribe's very reason for existence.
6.cn: 小黄人种族存在的意义就是为了让他们的主人开心。

7.en: Why did you bring me here? To find out who you told of our existence.
7.cn: 你为什么要带我来这？想了解你把我们的存在告诉了谁。

8.en: It gives proof to the existence of matter. Without time, we don't exist.
8.cn: 时间才是唯一的测量单位，没有时间，我们就不存在。

9.en: Time gives legitimacy to its existence. Time is the only true unit of measure.
9.cn: 时间就是存在的证明，时间才是唯一的测量单位。

10.en: We've codified our existence to bring it down to human size to make it comprehensible.
10.cn: 我们把自己的存在加以简化以方便人类理解。

11.en: Under no circumstances can he be made aware of my existence. You must promise me this.
11.cn: 他决不能知道我的存在，你要向我保证这一点。

12.en: Despite the risks of this collective existence, many species use the reef as a nursery.
12.cn: 尽管这种集体生活存在风险，很多物种还是将珊瑚礁作为了栖息地。

13.en: The Expansion the reason for my very existence would be over, so I did what I had to do.
13.cn: 这个扩张计划我存在的理由将毁于一旦，所以我做了我该做的事儿。

14.en: Humans consider themselves unique, so they rooted their whole theory of existence on their uniqueness.
14.cn: 人类总以为自己是独特的，存在理论总是以独特性为基础。

15.en: Everything that lives around us suffers from our existence. We leave footprints everywhere we go.
15.cn: 身边的一切都因为我们的存在而遭受痛苦，我们所到之处都留下脚印。

16.en: Their very existence is a threat. Is that clear, Commander? Clear, sir. Good. Carry on, Colonel.
16.cn: 他们的存在就是个威胁，明白吗，指挥官？明白，很好，请继续，上校。

17.en: No, but your ability to perceive their existence is conditional on you passing the second and third barriers.
17.cn: 不，但对你来说卧室的存在是有条件的，你要通过第二和第三关。

18.en: We're talking about a being whose very existence challenges our own sense of priority in the universe.
18.cn: 我们现在在讨论的这个人，他的存在挑战了我们自身对事物优先级别的认知。

19.en: So, how you been? Well, my existence is a continuum, so I've been what I am at each point in the implied time period.
19.cn: 你最近怎样？我的存在是个连续统一体，所以在指定期间的每个时间点都是一样的。
